```dockerfile
FROM node:18-slim AS frontend-builder

WORKDIR /build/frontend

COPY frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json ./
RUN npm ci

COPY frontend/ .
RUN npm run build

FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./
RUN pip install poetry && \
    poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-dev --no-interaction --no-ansi

FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="Analytics Platform Team" \
      description="Production-grade analytics platform with React frontend and Flask backend"

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN useradd -m -u 1000 superset

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=python-builder /build/.venv /app/.venv
COPY --from=frontend-builder /build/frontend/dist ./static

COPY . .

ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH"
ENV PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1

RUN chown -R superset:superset /app

USER superset

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
